# Sioyek Keys Configuration - Custom keybindings
#
# Theme switching:
# w - Toggle between Gruvbox light and Nord dark themes
#     Uses external script with state tracking for true toggle behavior
#     State persists within session; startup always uses Gruvbox (default)

_toggle_theme w
zoom_in K
zoom_out J

# Vim-style scroll keybindings (screen_down/up - no half-page in sioyek):
screen_down <C-d>
screen_up <C-u>

# Disabled keybindings:
# Ctrl+t - Default binding creates new instance, not needed
noop <C-t>
